Instruction
-----------------------------
Need to run the batch file and will run in the console

In Order to run the project 
Please go to the package com.canvas.drawing.main
and Run the CanvasMain.java file as Java Application Console.

OR 

Simply run the drawcanvas.bat file

Assumptions : 
---------------------
Diagonal Line Validation : Validate the LIne whether the user entered Diagonal Line which is not allowed on making Rectangles and Lines

Line and Point Bound Validation : Validate the line and point bound parameter so that it is within the bound of the Canvas

Requirements
----------------------
Java 8
TOMCAT SERVER or PIVOT SERVER
